content:
Test Data Cloud Features in a Sandbox (Beta)

You can access Data Cloud features in the same sandbox org that you use for testing, staging, and training. When you create a sandbox, all your production org Data Cloud metadata and configurations are replicated in the sandbox.

This change applies to Data Cloud in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions. The production org must have a Data Cloud license.

Note: Data Cloud in Sandbox is a pilot or beta service subject to Beta Services Terms. Use of this feature is at the Customer's sole discretion.

When: This functionality is available in July 2024.
title: Test Data Cloud Features in a Sandbox Beta
